item.title: UKRAINE HAS USED ITS GOD-GIVEN TALENTS TO DRIVE AGENDAS, NOT BURY THEM
item.description: **Message from the Chairman of the Australian Federation of Ukrainian Organisations – ** Stefan Romaniw OAM On the occasion of the 27th Anniversary of Ukraine’s Independence Embassy of Ukraine – 27 September 2018 My Lord Bishops, Reverend Fathers, Your Excellency Ambassador of Ukraine in Australia Mr Kulinich and Mrs Kulinich, Members of the Diplomatic and Consular Corps, Representatives of the Australian Parliament, Members of the Australian Federation of Ukrainian Organisations, ladies and gentlemen.
